HPSV Studio Works

MMCOE CANTEEN

Nestled in the vibrant city of Pune, the MMCOE Canteen serves as a bustling hub for culinary delights within the MMCOE campus. Located in the heart of Pune, this canteen offers a diverse menu of delicious and affordable meals, catering to the diverse tastes of students and faculty alike. With a comfortable and inviting ambiance, the MMCOE Canteen provides a social space for students to gather, unwind, and enjoy a variety of flavorful dishes. Whether it's a quick bite between classes or a leisurely meal with friends, the MMCOE Canteen in Pune stands as a cherished spot for community and culinary satisfaction within the MMCOE campus.

LOHEGAON BUNGALOW

Located in the heart of Lohegaon, Pune, this expansive 4,700 sq ft bungalow is an embodiment of tranquility and style. Nestled amidst lush greenery, its refined design, featuring expansive windows, bathes the interiors in natural light. The uncomplicated layout effortlessly unfolds to reveal a charming deck and a meticulously groomed lawn, creating an idyllic space for a serene and relaxed lifestyle.

INDAPUR BUNGALOW

Located in Indapur, this 4000 sq. ft. bungalow seamlessly integrates modern design with the serene beauty of its surroundings. The spacious interiors and thoughtful layout create a comfortable living space, perfect for relaxation and enjoyment. With ample room for both privacy and socializing, this home in Indapur offers a harmonious blend of style and tranquility. Explore the charm of this residence, where every corner reflects a balance between contemporary living and the peaceful ambiance of its location. Indulge in the comfort and sophistication of this uniquely crafted bungalow in the heart of Indapur.

LOHEGAON BUNGALOW

Situated in the quaint locale of Kalwad, Pune, this expansive 5500 square feet bungalow stands as a testament to luxury living. Boasting a prime location, the residence harmoniously combines spacious design with modern aesthetics. Each corner of this meticulously crafted bungalow reflects a perfect blend of comfort and sophistication, making it an ideal haven for residents. With ample space for diverse living requirements and a touch of elegance in every detail, this Kalwad-based bungalow promises a lifestyle of unparalleled refinement and tranquility. Experience the epitome of luxurious living in this grand 5500 sq. ft. residence nestled in the heart of Pune's Kalwad.

INTERIOR

Situated in the vibrant locale of Bhosari, Pune, Classic Enterprises is set to undergo a transformative interior redesign by HPSV. The project aims to infuse timeless elegance into the workspace, blending functionality with sophistication. Expect a harmonious fusion of modern design elements and classic aesthetics, creating an inviting ambiance conducive to productivity and creativity. HPSV's expertise promises to craft an interior that not only reflects the professionalism of Classic Enterprises but also provides a conducive and inspiring environment for both clients and employees alike. Get ready to witness a refined and distinctive workspace that stands as a testament to Bhosari's business culture.
